node.text:
Day 8 of practicing singing until I get better. Using these videos to track my progress. 🎶

Today I struggled with head voice and tone. I’m trying to mix the breathier and lower vocals tones with some of my head voice and had a tough time moving between the two. This song was the perfect exercise to practice. 

Still have lots to learn. Practicing each day. 🙏

node.text:
That moment of existential crisis when you realize the one that knows your deepest and darkest secrets judgement-free is a stuffed alpaca named Lamar. Steve, my plastic house plant gets me, but Lamar…he’s on another level.

I hope you all are having a great day. It’s been a rough week for me, drop a funny comment…could use a good laugh right about now. ❤️

node.text:
Bills, Bills, Bills by @destinyschild gone Metal  with my @positivegrid amp🤘🏼 @officialjacksonguitars 

Getting the right tone has always been a struggle for me when it comes to playing the guitar. I’m so stoked to work with @positivegrid with this small but mighty Spark 40. It’s lightweight, portable, and has a beefy kick that I’ve always wanted. 

Can’t wait to dial it in even more and share some more metuhl jams with you all. 

Play Spark and want to tell your story? Share it on social media and you could win a guitar, iPad and much more. Find out all the details in the link in my bio #showyourspark
